## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Java 11 or higher
- Gradle 8.5+

### Build and Run
```bash
# Build the project
./gradlew build

# Create executable JAR
./gradlew shadowJar

# Run the application
java -jar build/libs/usagi.jar
```

